## 5. Information Architecture

```
/                                    → Home (Deck Grid + Search + Filters)
/decks/:id                           → Individual Deck Viewer
/reveals/:id/v{n}.html               → Raw Reveal.js HTML (iframe source, versioned)
content/decks/*.md                   → Deck metadata (Nuxt Content, not a route)
```

