## 8. UI Component Specifications

### 8.1 DeckCard

- Dimensions: 280–320px width, auto height
- Thumbnail area: Solid color gradient using deck's primary tag color
- Content padding: 16px
- Title: Plus Jakarta Sans 600, 15px, `text-gray-900` / `text-gray-100` (dark)
- Description: Plus Jakarta Sans 400, 13px, `text-gray-600`, 2-line clamp
- Tags: 11px, `bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-700` / `bg-emerald-900/20 text-emerald-300` (dark)
- Hover: `border-color` transition 150ms to `border-gray-300`
- Focus: 2px solid Emerald ring
- Click target: Entire card is the `<NuxtLink>` (not just the title)

### 8.2 SearchBar

- Height: 44px (meets WCAG 2.5.8 target size)
- Border-radius: 8px
- Placeholder: "Search by title, description, or tags..."
- Focus: 2px solid Emerald outline
- Debounce: 300ms before triggering filter
- Clear button (×): Appears when input has value

### 8.3 FilterTags

- Chip height: 32px, padding: 4px 12px
- Active: `bg-emerald-600 text-white`
- Inactive: `bg-gray-100 text-gray-700` / `bg-gray-800 text-gray-300` (dark)
- Badge count: `bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-800` pill, 11px
- Overflow: Horizontal scroll on mobile, wrap on desktop
- `aria-pressed="true|false"` on each chip

### 8.4 DeckViewer (iframe)

- Aspect ratio: 16:9, clamped at min-height 400px
- Border: 1px solid `border-gray-200`
- Border-radius: 8px (with `overflow: hidden`)
- Controls below: Prev / Slide Counter / Next / Fullscreen
- Button size: 44×44px minimum

### 8.5 DeckSidebar

- Width: 280–320px (desktop), full-width (mobile)
- Position: `sticky`, top: 80px
- Sections: Description → Tags → Version History → Statistics → Actions
- Section dividers: 1px `border-gray-200`
- Event history: Comma-separated list of event names from `events[]`

### 8.6 VersionSelector

- Visibility: Hidden when `versions.length === 1`; rendered below the viewer controls when `versions.length > 1`
- Dropdown label: "Version" with current selection shown
- Option format: `"v{n} — {label} · {date}"` (e.g., "v2 — OrlandoCodeCamp26 Update · Mar 2026")
- Default selection: `currentVersion` from frontmatter
- Changelog: If selected version has `changes` field, render as muted text (13px, `text-gray-500`) below dropdown
- Height: 44px (WCAG 2.5.8 target size)
- Focus: 2px solid Emerald ring
- `aria-label="Select presentation version"`

